metadata.description:
Dumb Wojapes are 6969 satirical generative digital artworks on the Ethereum blockchain produced by Bofa Labs and a shady cartel of undoxxed developers. Each Wojape is unique and special, just like you. Owning a Dumb Wojape entitles you to infinite joy and positivity that you can feel from looking at it with a good attitude. Wojapes are made with over 500 different traits. 

Some Wojapes are sharing their unique seed phrase which was randomly generated at mint. 

All original Dumb Wojape artwork is CC0 and in the public domain.
metadata.name: Wojape #1
